944	This section packages the standard basic-open cover of an affine open into the project's conventions. Given a subset $s \subseteq \mathcal O_X(U)$ spanning the unit ideal, the basic opens $D(f)$ for $f \in s$ form a cover of $U$. All members and their finite intersections are again affine.
